text:
#COVIDUpdates: In AP, out of 8,72,076 samples tested for #COVID19 13,891 tested positive. From the total positives, 6,232 got recovered and 180 deceased. 7,479 people are undertaking treatment in #COVID care centres and hospitals.
#APFightsCorona #COVID19Pandemic https://t.co/i7qLaskMnc
